<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>9534</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>20369</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“大家请注意，因为大雪，今天学校两点放学。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>20369</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>24033</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>广播里传出弗拉尼校长的声音，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>24033</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>28463</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“希望大家能够安全回家。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>28463</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>35807</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>尼娜在二年级教室里想：“今天还会有儿童中心活动吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>35807</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>40984</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>贾森在三年级教室里也在想同样的事。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>40984</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>46942</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>就在这时，雪莉老师从门口把头伸了进来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>46942</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>50223</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“今天儿童中心两点开始活动。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>50223</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>55238</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>大家一直待到父母来接你们，好吗？” 她说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>55238</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>60182</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>贾森点点头，波比竖起大拇指。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>60182</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>67013</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“尼娜、莉琪、波比，你们的妈妈刚刚打电话过来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>67013</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>70799</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她们四点到。” 雪莉老师说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>70799</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>76124</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们有足够的活动时间。你们带围裙来了吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>76124</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>82132</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我爸爸呢？” 贾森问，“他什么时候来？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>82132</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>86898</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>贾森的爸爸每个星期三都来接他。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>86898</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>91530</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后他们会一起去吃披萨。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>91530</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>95851</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你爸爸还没有打电话过来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>95851</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>102453</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是别担心，他一定会像平时一样五点到的。” 雪莉老师说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>102453</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>108711</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“今天我们要做雪花巧克力蛋糕。” 雪莉老师说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>108711</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>113177</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“耶！巧克力蛋糕。” 莉琪说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>113177</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>118325</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“但什么是雪花巧克力蛋糕呢？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>118325</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>122407</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>贾森没有听到雪莉老师的回答。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>122407</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>125646</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他还在想自己的爸爸。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>125646</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>130000</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>为什么他还没有打电话来呢？</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>130000</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>136516</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“第一步：把烤箱预热到175摄氏度。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>136516</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>141594</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>贾森，你可以帮忙吗？” 雪莉老师问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>141594</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>145039</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“什么？哦，好的。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>145039</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>148925</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>贾森在烤箱上设置了温度。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>148925</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>153718</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“第二步：在烤盘上抹油。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>153718</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>159714</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>雪莉老师，这次可以让我抹油吗？” 尼娜问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>159714</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>170155</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“当然可以。给你油和纸巾。” 老师说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>170155</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>173267</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“谁要念第三步？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>173267</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>179587</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我！第三步：把融化的黄油和糖混合起来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>179587</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>187904</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>请给我糖。” 莉琪伸手拿糖。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>187904</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>191849</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“第四步。” 波比念道，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>191849</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>201169</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“加入鸡蛋和香草香精。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>201169</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>207829</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“第五步：加入可可粉和面粉。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>207829</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>215457</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>你好呀，贾森！你可以把面粉倒进去吗？” 尼娜问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>215457</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>219949</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“第六步：加入盐和发酵粉。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>219949</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>226832</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>莉琪加入盐和发酵粉。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>226832</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>233668</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“可以烤了！” 雪莉老师把烤盘放进烤箱。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>233668</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>237322</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“等27分钟就可以了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>237322</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>242697</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>这段时间，孩子们量了一下窗户上的积雪。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>242697</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>248322</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这里是12厘米！” 莉琪大喊。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>248322</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>256414</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“现在该把它们变成雪花巧克力蛋糕了。” 雪莉老师说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>256414</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>261086</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>孩子们把纸做的雪花放在烤盘上方。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>261086</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>264961</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>雪莉老师在上面撒上糖粉。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>264961</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>271969</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>当孩子们把纸拿走时，蛋糕上就有了漂亮的雪花图案。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>271969</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>274320</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>五点多了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>274320</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>281617</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>大家都走了以后，雪莉老师和贾森清理桌子，洗了碗。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>281617</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>285195</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们又一起看了一本书。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>285195</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>290101</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>六点的时候，体育馆的门开了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>290101</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>294603</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“好香啊。” 一个男人说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>294603</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>299878</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“爸爸！” 贾森跳起来，跑向爸爸。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>299878</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>302697</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“对不起，我来晚了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>302697</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>307552</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我在开会，不能用手机。” 他的爸爸说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>56</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>307552</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>309664</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“准备好回家了吗？</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>57</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>309664</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>313773</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>今天雪太大，我们不能去吃披萨了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>58</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>313773</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>324523</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“没关系。我们可以吃巧克力蛋糕！” 贾森说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>